# Cloudflare Pages — SPA fallback
# All requests that don't match a real file get served index.html with a 200.
# This is what makes /series/berserk work when the user navigates directly
# or refreshes the page — without this, Cloudflare would return a 404.

/privacy   /privacy.html  200
/series/*  /index.html    200
/*         /index.html
